But...I'm afraid we're looking at fairly widespread damage.

238
00:15:54,048 --> 00:15:56,014
那是什么意思?
What does that mean?

239
00:15:56,015 --> 00:16:01,066
意思是她的生命要靠这些仪器维持
It means that right now these machines are sustaining her life.

240
00:16:01,067 --> 00:16:04,049
但不会一直...
But it won't always be...

241
00:16:04,050 --> 00:16:05,098
当她醒来 她不会...
I mean, when she wakes up, she won't...

242
00:16:05,099 --> 00:16:09,077
我不能很肯定的告诉你
I can't say with any real confidence

243
00:16:09,078 --> 00:16:14,092
她会醒过来
that she will wake up.

244
00:16:27,031 --> 00:16:28,088
她能听见我们吗?
Can she hear us?

245
00:16:28,089 --> 00:16:30,085
我希望是这样
I like to think she can.

246
00:16:30,086 --> 00:16:33,019
她这样要多久?
How long will she be like this?

247
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:35,063
也许一天 一个星期或是一年
Could be a day, a week or years.

248
00:16:35,064 --> 00:16:38,027
我们只能等待
We'll just have to wait and see.

249
00:16:38,028 --> 00:16:40,084
但我能保证你们她会受到很好的照顾的
But I can assure you, she'll be well looked after.

250
00:16:40,085 --> 00:16:44,070
那很好 只是我们付不起那么多
Oh, that's very nice, but we can't pay for that.

251
00:16:44,071 --> 00:16:51,044
别担心 有人已经帮你们解决了
Don't worry. Her expenses have already been taken care of.

252
00:16:53,003 --> 00:16:54,086
是谁?
By whom?

253
