他让我保密
I've been asked to keep that confidential.

254
00:17:20,042 --> 00:17:25,004
1... 2...
One... Two...

255
00:17:29,009 --> 00:17:32,030
不!
No!

256
00:17:36,012 --> 00:17:37,081
我很抱歉
Look, I'm sorry.

257
00:17:37,086 --> 00:17:39,078
我很抱歉 伙计
I'm sorry, man.

258
00:17:40,023 --> 00:17:41,010
我很抱歉
I said I'm sorry.

259
00:17:41,011 --> 00:17:42,012
你到底想干什么?
What the hell is wrong with you?

260
00:17:42,013 --> 00:17:44,066
