I was shooting at a boar. I had no idea you were out here.

261
00:17:44,067 --> 00:17:46,008
Charlie在哪里?
Where's Charlie?

262
00:17:46,088 --> 00:17:47,068
他在营地里
He's back at the camp.

263
00:17:47,069 --> 00:17:48,025
我很抱歉吓到了你们...
I'm really sorry if I frightened...

264
00:17:48,026 --> 00:17:51,012
所以就你一个人?
So it's just you?

265
00:17:51,099 --> 00:17:56,077
你就正好出现在我们设陷阱的地方?
Hunting, in the exact same spot as we're setting our trap?

266
00:17:56,078 --> 00:17:58,079
我在追一头野猪 Claire
I was following a boar, Claire.

267
00:17:58,080 --> 00:18:03,003
那可真是巧啊
So it's just a coincidence, then.

268
00:18:03,004 --> 00:18:05,090
那头猪呢?
Where is it?

269
00:18:05,091 --> 00:18:10,005
它跑了
It got away.

270
00:18:13,037 --> 00:18:15,086
你不想让我捉住那只鸟是吗?
You don't want me to catch the birds, do you?

271
00:18:15,087 --> 00:18:19,058
你和Charlie 到底怎么了?
You and Charlie..what's going on?

272
00:18:19,059 --> 00:18:25,049
我为什么不想你捉住它?
Why wouldn't I want you to catch the birds?

273
00:18:36,081 --> 00:18:38,043
