What are these pylons?

277
00:18:50,029 --> 00:18:54,099
你认为呢?
What do you think they are?

278
00:18:55,028 --> 00:18:57,059
一种区域防御系统
A security perimeter.

279
00:18:57,060 --> 00:19:00,034
任何人走进去时
Those sensors on the side would be triggered

280
00:19:00,035 --> 00:19:06,032
就会触发陷阱
if anyone passed between them.

281
00:19:06,033 --> 00:19:09,031
这是警报系统或是陷阱
It's an alarm system or a trap.

282
00:19:09,032 --> 00:19:11,056
我们在这里会很安全
Either way, we'll be safer going around it.

283
00:19:11,057 --> 00:19:15,028
你是对的 这是个防御系统
You are right. It was a security perimeter,

284
00:19:15,029 --> 00:19:18,071
