but like everything else on this island, it hasn't functioned in years.

285
00:19:18,072 --> 00:19:22,040
别耍我们了
Of course it hasn't.

286
00:19:22,041 --> 00:19:25,032
如果你想浪费时间 随便你
If you wish to waste your time, be my guest.

287
00:19:25,033 --> 00:19:28,036
