The pylons encircle the entire barracks.

288
00:19:28,037 --> 00:19:30,077
你们这样是进不去的
There is no going around them.

289
00:19:30,078 --> 00:19:36,005
如果你不相信我的话 看看你的地图
If you don't believe me, look at your map.

290
00:19:46,009 --> 00:19:52,050
