Why are you really here?

307
00:21:19,041 --> 00:21:21,092
是为了Jack吗?
Are you here for Jack?

308
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:24,079
那还有什么原因?
Why else would I be here?

309
00:21:25,023 --> 00:21:27,041
这事我们稍后再解决
We'll talk about this later.

310
00:21:27,042 --> 00:21:29,015
我同意
Fine by me.

311
