那我们怎么穿过去?
Just tell me how we're gonna go through this.

312
00:21:30,046 --> 00:21:32,037
我们另找办法
We're not gonna go through it.

313
00:21:32,038 --> 00:21:34,084
我们翻过去
We're going over it.

314
00:21:35,066 --> 00:21:36,089
Sayid, 斧头放在哪了?
Sayid, where's the axe?

315
00:21:36,090 --> 00:21:38,043
在他的背包里
It's in his pack.

316
00:21:38,044 --> 00:21:39,061
等等 我来拿
No, wait a minute. I got it.

317
00:21:39,062 --> 00:21:41,090
我来吧
Here, I got it.

318
00:21:52,028 --> 00:21:55,062
我认为你原来不知道有C-4的
I thought you didn't know there was any c-4.

319
00:21:55,093 --> 00:21:58,050
好吧 我承认
Well, I stand corrected.

320
00:21:58,051 --> 00:22:00,081
你为什么带上它?
Why did you take it?

321
00:22:00,082 --> 00:22:04,035
你永远不知道小小的C-4也许能派上用处
You never know when a little c-4 might come in handy.

322
00:22:04,078 --> 00:22:07,061
