343
00:23:13,009 --> 00:23:15,006
反应过度?
Overreacting?

344
00:23:15,007 --> 00:23:18,049
不 我以为我能和你在一起 我能依赖你
No, I thought you were here for me, that I could count on you.

345
00:23:18,050 --> 00:23:19,031
