I was wrong.

346
00:23:19,032 --> 00:23:20,019
不 Claire
No, Claire!

347
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:23,076
我还是靠我自己吧 至少现在我意识到了
I'm on my own, and at least I know that now.

348
00:23:23,077 --> 00:23:24,041
Claire

