What are you doing here?

363
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,043
我才要走 Lindsey
I was just on my way out, Lindsey.

364
00:24:31,044 --> 00:24:33,009
如果Carole知道你在这里...
If Carole knew you were here...

365
