00:25:01,012 --> 00:25:03,058
是你付的医疗费?
Are you the one paying the bills?

377
00:25:03,059 --> 00:25:06,081
是你照料这些事的?
Are you the one taking care of all this?

378
00:25:09,027 --> 00:25:11,089
是的
Yes.

379
00:25:17,050 --> 00:25:20,029
那你是谁?
Then who are you?

380
00:25:25,049 --> 00:25:28,068
我是你的父亲 Claire
I'm your father, Claire.

381
00:26:04,015 --> 00:26:06,088
如果有东西切断了系统的水平面
The system appears to fire a sonic pulse

382
00:26:06,089 --> 00:26:09,055
那就会触发电磁回路
when an object breaks the plane between two pylons.

383
00:26:09,056 --> 00:26:11,068
所以
So...

384
00:26:11,069 --> 00:26:15,037
只要我们不去碰那个水平面 我们就会没事的
as long as we don't break the plane, we should remain unharmed.

385
00:26:15,038 --> 00:26:17,044
为什么不用炸药呢?
Why not just use the plastic explosive you took?

386
00:26:17,045 --> 00:26:20,024
你想死就随便你
Be my guest. You wanna go stick it on there?

387
00:26:20,025 --> 00:26:23,068
谁爬过去后 给一个安全信号
Whoever climbs over, give those sensors a wide berth.

388
00:26:23,069 --> 00:26:26,021
我先来
I'll go first.

389
00:26:29,050 --> 00:26:31,077
帮我一把
Give me a hand.

390
00:27:32,016 --> 00:27:34,088
我想我是第二个
I guess I'll go next.

391
00:28:09,066 --> 00:28:11,038
行了
Here you go.

392
00:28:11,039 --> 00:28:13,058
谢谢
Thanks.

393
00:28:16,015 --> 00:28:17,094
不要为那事烦心了
You have every right to be upset.

394
00:28:17,095 --> 00:28:20,046
这一点都没道理
It just doesn't make any sense.

395
00:28:20,047 --> 00:28:23,024
Desmond从没打过野猪
Desmond's never gone boar hunting before,

396
00:28:23,025 --> 00:28:25,029
而野猪也不会那么靠近海滩
and the boar never come that close to the beach.

397
00:28:25,030 --> 00:28:27,087
不管发生了什么
Well, whatever is going on,

398
00:28:27,088 --> 00:28:30,068
他们还在那边说话呢
they're still talking about it.

399
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:38,063
你能看一下他吗?
Can you watch him?

400
00:28:38,064 --> 00:28:41,003
你要去干什么?
What are you going to do?

401
00:28:42,050 --> 00:28:45,034
找出答案
Get some answers.

402
00:28:50,073 --> 00:28:53,039
一会儿就来
I'll be with you in a sec.

403
00:28:56,094 --> 00:28:59,006
行了
There you go.

404
00:28:59,007 --> 00:29:01,067
10块钱
It'll be 10 bucks.

405
00:29:11,097 --> 00:29:13,092
你来这儿干嘛?
What are you doing here?

406
00:29:13,093 --> 00:29:16,083
请你喝杯咖啡?
Buy you a cup of coffee?

407
00:29:18,095 --> 00:29:20,049
我和你没什么好说的
I have nothing to say to you.

408
00:29:20,050 --> 00:29:23,088
Claire今晚我就离开 从此我会从你的生活中消失的
I'm leaving tonight, then I'll be out of your life forever.

409
00:29:23,089 --> 00:29:28,043
就一杯咖啡
Just one cup of coffee.

410
00:29:35,036 --> 00:29:38,008
这都是真的
So it's true.

411
00:29:38,052 --> 00:29:42,030
是的
Yes, it's true.

412
00:29:47,024 --> 00:29:49,062
你是怎么知道发生事故了?
How'd you find out about the accident?

413
00:29:49,063 --> 00:29:51,049
一个在悉尼的朋友告诉我的
A doctor friend here in Sydney told me.

414
00:29:51,050 --> 00:29:55,092
你母亲一进手术室我就接到了电话
I got the call the minute your mother went into surgery.

415
00:29:58,034 --> 00:30:01,045
为什么她告诉我你死了?
Why did she tell me that you're dead?

416
00:30:02,031 --> 00:30:08,019
是因为我和她在一起留下了许多美好的时光吧
Well, because I..no doubt...left her with so many wonderful memories.

417
00:30:09,089 --> 00:30:12,078
我们有段美妙的时光
Look, we had a fling.

418
00:30:12,079 --> 00:30:15,072
我回络杉矶后她才告诉我她怀孕了
I was back in Los Angeles when she told me that she was pregnant,

419
00:30:15,073 --> 00:30:18,053
她将有个还孩子 你
that she was going to have the baby...have you.

420
00:30:18,054 --> 00:30:21,018
你不想见我?
You didn't want to see me?

421
00:30:21,019 --> 00:30:25,067
不 在你小的时候我来看过你几次
No. I came out a bunch of times when you were little.

422
00:30:25,068 --> 00:30:29,089
我过来买玩具给你
I stayed over,gave you toys.

423
00:30:29,090 --> 00:30:32,064
给你唱歌
I sang to you.

424
00:30:34,027 --> 00:30:37,016
为什么你后来不来了呢?
Why'd you stop coming?

425
00:30:37,098 --> 00:30:40,009
因为你的姨妈恨我
'cause your aunt hates me,

426
00:30:40,010 --> 00:30:42,078
而你母亲不愿意接受
and your mother didn't like the fact that...

427
00:30:42,079 --> 00:30:45,033
我有另外一个家庭的现实
I had another family.

428
00:30:45,034 --> 00:30:47,061
那你现在来做什么?
Why are you here now, then? Why'd you come?

429
00:30:47,062 --> 00:30:49,093
就为了给我们付医疗费?
You could've just paid her bills from the states.

430
00:30:49,094 --> 00:30:53,006
我来是想帮助你们
I came over because I wanted to help.

431
00:30:53,007 --> 00:30:55,045
帮助什么?
Help with what?

432
00:30:55,046 --> 00:30:59,089
Claire 你母亲还活着
Your mother is alive...

433
00:31:01,046 --> 00:31:04,006
但基本上是个植物人
but she's not really living.

434
00:31:04,007 --> 00:31:05,035
你到底什么意思?
What that's supposed to mean?

435
00:31:05,036 --> 00:31:09,046
意思是是时候选择
It means that now may be the time

436
00:31:09,047 --> 00:31:12,039
其它的道路来减轻她的痛苦
to look at other alternatives, other ways to relieve her pain.

437
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:15,009
撤掉她身上的仪器是非法的
Now it is illegal to turn off her machines,

438
00:31:15,010 --> 00:31:19,033
但我知道一种合法的办法
but I know of ways that can achieve the same effect without the legal consequences.

439
00:31:19,034 --> 00:31:20,095
闭嘴!
Just stop it!

440
00:31:20,096 --> 00:31:23,023
你不是来帮我的
You didn't come here to help me.

441
00:31:23,024 --> 00:31:25,088
你是来弥补自己的过失的
You came here to try and fix a mistake that you made.

442
00:31:25,089 --> 00:31:26,092
不 亲爱的 不是这样的
No, honey, that's not true.

443
00:31:26,093 --> 00:31:30,067
你以为付了医疗费就能让你变成一个高尚的人吗?
You think that just paying her bills makes you noble or something?

444
00:31:31,012 --> 00:31:36,002
你来这里是想杀死她?
You come down here, and you try and get me to kill her?

445
00:31:39,019 --> 00:31:40,086
你走吧
You know, just go.

446
00:31:40,087 --> 00:31:41,074
为什么你不走呢?
Why don't you just go?

447
00:31:41,075 --> 00:31:44,088
回到你真实的家庭去
Go back to your real family.

448
00:31:47,041 --> 00:31:49,072
你知道
You know

449
00:31:50,063 --> 00:31:53,066
你也许是我的父亲
You might be my father

450
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:58,093
但我甚至都不知道你的名字
But I don't even know your name...

451
00:31:59,045 --> 00:32:03,092
而我也不想知道
And I, um, I want it to stay that way.

452
00:32:03,093 --> 00:32:05,037
Claire...Claire

453
00:32:05,038 --> 00:32:06,048
Claire听我说
Listen to me.

454
00:32:06,049 --> 00:32:08,064
听我说
Listen to me.

455
00:32:08,065 --> 00:32:12,023
别让你母亲以错误的原因活下去
Do not keep your mother alive for the wrong reasons.

456
00:32:12,024 --> 00:32:15,083
希望还是罪责 相信我
Now there is hope and there is guilt, and believe me,

457
00:32:15,084 --> 00:32:19,015
我知道这的区别
I know the difference.

458
00:32:26,022 --> 00:32:28,018
再见了 孩子
Good-bye, kiddo.

459
00:32:28,019 --> 00:32:30,090
很高兴再次见到你
It's great seeing you again.

460
00:33:13,034 --> 00:33:16,005
你到底在做什么?
What the hell are you doing?

461
00:33:16,010 --> 00:33:18,069
你跟踪我
You followed me.

462
00:33:19,095 --> 00:33:22,002
退后!
Stay back!

463
00:33:22,003 --> 00:33:23,027
这有只鸟
It's one of the birds.

464
00:33:23,028 --> 00:33:25,094
退后!
Stay back!

465
00:33:43,039 --> 00:33:45,035
你怎么知道会在这里的?
How did you know it was gonna be here?

466
00:33:45,036 --> 00:33:46,089
我不知道
I didn't.

467
00:33:46,090 --> 00:33:48,047
是的 你知道
Yes, you did.

468
00:33:48,048 --> 00:33:50,018
你一定知道
You had to.

469
00:33:50,019 --> 00:33:53,049
这就是你和Charlie争执的事情
That's what you and Charlie were arguing about.

470
00:33:54,073 --> 00:33:57,026
你知道的
You knew.

471
00:33:57,053 --> 00:33:58,022
我怎么会知道?
How would I?

472
00:33:58,023 --> 00:34:01,063
你不去任何地方找
I don't know, but you know,you walked straight here

473
00:34:01,064 --> 00:34:04,009
就径直来到这里
no doubt at all about where you were going.

474
00:34:04,010 --> 00:34:08,018
在这片海滩这块石头
You came right to this beach and right to this rock,

475
00:34:08,019 --> 00:34:11,072
而且很巧的是 这有只鸟
and low and behold, there's the bird.

476
00:34:13,003 --> 00:34:16,053
到底发生了什么 Desmond?
What t hell is going on, Desmond?

477
00:34:23,042 --> 00:34:26,067
看见那块地方了吗?
See that spot over there?

478
00:34:29,070 --> 00:34:33,016
那就是Charlie滑倒的地方
That's where Charlie slipped and fell in.

479
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:37,029
他撞在石头上
He got pounded again and again by the rocks and

480
00:34:37,033 --> 00:34:39,059
摔断了他的脖子
broke his neck.

481
00:34:39,060 --> 00:34:41,046
什么?
What?

482
00:34:41,047 --> 00:34:44,091
你在说什么?
What...what are you talking about?

483
00:34:44,092 --> 00:34:48,026
那就是Charlie死的地方
That's where Charlie died.

484
00:35:01,096 --> 00:35:04,050
看Desmond找到了什么
Look what Desmond found.

485
00:35:04,051 --> 00:35:07,017
太好了
How about that?

486
00:35:07,024 --> 00:35:09,020
真的有标签啊
It does have a tag.

487
00:35:09,021 --> 00:35:11,085
你是对的
You were right.

488
00:35:15,073 --> 00:35:18,076
Desmond把一切都告诉我了
Desmond told me everything

489
00:35:20,086 --> 00:35:23,081
那些幻觉
about all his visions

490
00:35:24,029 --> 00:35:27,097
他知道你会被电击
That he knew you were gonna get hit by lightning,

491
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:35,005
为了救我你会淹死
that you were gonna drown trying to rescue me in the ocean

492
00:35:38,078 --> 00:35:42,008
为了捉这只鸟 你摔死了
how you died trying to get me this bird.

493
00:35:42,009 --> 00:35:45,031
你不会相信的 是吧?
You don't believe all that, do you?

494
00:36:09,008 --> 00:36:11,043
谁把电视关了?
Now who turned the telly off?

495
00:36:11,044 --> 00:36:14,095
他们不知道我妈妈喜欢看自然节目吗?
Don't they know how much you love your nature shows?

496
00:36:17,021 --> 00:36:19,091
这样好多了
That's better.

497
00:36:22,023 --> 00:36:25,021
妈妈 你今天怎么样?
So how are you today, mum?

498
00:36:25,022 --> 00:36:28,030
睡的好吗?
Did you have an okay night?

499
00:36:41,019 --> 00:36:44,000
我...
Listen...

500
00:36:44,067 --> 00:36:47,080
要告诉你一些事
Something I have to tell you,

501
00:36:47,081 --> 00:36:51,081
一些我很早就应该告诉你的事
something I should have told you a long time ago.

502
00:36:58,089 --> 00:37:01,080
我怀孕了
I'm pregnant.

503
00:37:06,052 --> 00:37:10,057
我要把他送走
I'm giving it away.

504
00:37:11,073 --> 00:37:15,007
这样做最好
It's for the best.

505
00:37:20,067 --> 00:37:23,071
最好是这样
I wish...

506
00:37:28,018 --> 00:37:31,020
我不知道你怎么...
I don't know how you did it...

507
00:37:31,021 --> 00:37:34,046
独自把我抚养大的
raising me alone.

508
00:37:34,047 --> 00:37:38,015
一定很艰难
That must have been so hard,

509
00:37:38,067 --> 00:37:40,070
而我真是...
and I was just...

510
00:37:40,071 --> 00:37:43,055
一团糟
awful...

511
00:37:44,002 --> 00:37:47,004
糟透了
awful...

512
00:37:47,045 --> 00:37:50,082
让你操心了
So horrible to you.

513
00:37:55,005 --> 00:37:58,016
对不起 妈妈
I'm so sorry, mum.

514
00:38:01,015 --> 00:38:04,029
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry

515
00:38:07,015 --> 00:38:12,094
为了我在车里对你说的不好的话
So sorry for all the awful things I said to you in the car

516
00:38:13,076 --> 00:38:19,038
说我恨你
That...I hated you...

517
00:38:20,088 --> 00:38:24,002
说我不希望你是我的母亲
and that I wished you weren't my mother

518
00:38:24,003 --> 00:38:27,060
说我希望你死
and that I wished you were dead.

519
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:30,010
都是我的错
It's all my fault

520
00:38:30,011 --> 00:38:34,098
那场事故 所有一切
the accident, everything.

521
00:38:39,097 --> 00:38:43,064
我很抱歉 妈妈
I'm so sorry, mom.

522
00:38:43,065 --> 00:38:47,019
对不起
I'm so sorry.

523
00:38:49,037 --> 00:38:52,068
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

524
00:38:55,055 --> 00:38:59,024
我会回来看你的 好吗?
I'll see you soon, okay?

525
00:38:59,075 --> 00:39:06,059
我们是815航班的幸存者
To whom it may concern,we are survivors of Oceanic flight 815.

526
00:39:07,078 --> 00:39:11,094
我们已经在岛上待了80天了
We have survived on this island for 80 days.

527
00:39:12,065 --> 00:39:15,059
起飞后6小时
We were six hours into the flight when the pilot said we were off course

528
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:19,037
我们的飞机转向Fiji
and turned back towards Fiji.

529
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:23,075
接着撞毁在这座岛上
We hit turbulence and crashed.

530
00:39:23,076 --> 00:39:27,002
我们一直在这里等待救援
We've been waiting here all this time

531
00:39:27,003 --> 00:39:30,089
可就是没人来
waiting for rescue that has not come.

532
00:39:30,089 --> 00:39:32,007
我们不知道我们在哪儿
We do not know where we are.

533
00:39:32,008 --> 00:39:36,034
只知道你们找不到我们
We only know you have not found us.

534
00:39:36,049 --> 00:39:39,037
我们尽力在岛上生存下来
We've done our best to live on this island.

535
00:39:39,038 --> 00:39:43,060
有些人已经接受了没人救援的现实
Some of us have come to accept we may never leave it.

536
00:39:45,017 --> 00:39:49,004
飞机遇难后不是每个人都活了下来
Not all of us have survived since the crash,

537
00:39:49,006 --> 00:39:51,067
但也有新生命的诞生
but there is new life, too,

538
00:39:51,068 --> 00:39:54,087
这给了我们希望
and with it, there is hope.

539
00:39:54,088 --> 00:39:57,079
我们还活着
We are alive.

540
00:39:59,064 --> 00:40:02,062
请不要放弃我们
Please don't give up on us.

541
00:40:02,063 --> 00:40:05,040
这...
It's...

542
00:40:05,087 --> 00:40:09,021
真是完美Claire
It's perfect, Claire.

543
00:40:16,036 --> 00:40:20,005
我也不会放弃你的 Charlie
You know, I'm not giving up on you either, Charlie.

544
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:24,000
一切都会好起来的
It's gonna be okay.

545
00:40:24,001 --> 00:40:26,089
你也会没事的
You're gonna be okay.

546
00:40:31,059 --> 00:40:34,089
我们一起度过
We'll get through this together.

547
00:41:21,015 --> 00:41:23,076
怎么了?
What?

548
00:41:24,049 --> 00:41:27,035
我们到了
We're here.

